nd-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><font size=\"3\">So, if you are a direct-trade roaster who is interested in participating in this program, or a specialty coffee grower or consumer who would like to urge the roaster(s) you work with to participate, please go to the&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: underline; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><a href=\"http://www.transparenttradecoffee.org/#!faq/c8ns\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; cursor: pointer; color: inherit; background: transparent;\">Contact Page</a></span>&nbsp;or the&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: underline; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><a href=\"http://www.transparenttradecoffee.org/#!join/cee5\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; cursor: pointer; color: inherit; background: transparent;\">Register Page</a></span>.</font></span></span></p><p class=\"font_9\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: helvetica-w01-roman, helvetica-w02-roman, helvetica-lt-w10-roman, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 63, 63); text-align: justify; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;</p><p class=\"font_9\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: helvetica-w01-roman, helvetica-w02-roman, helvetica-lt-w10-roman, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 63, 63); text-align: justify; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5em; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif; background: transparent;\"></span></span></p><p class=\"font_9\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: helvetica-w01-roman, helvetica-w02-roman, helvetica-lt-w10-roman, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 63, 63); text-align: justify; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: italic; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif; background: transparent;\">[1] Effective grower share is calculated by dividing the price (f.o.b.) paid to growers by the green-pound equivalent price charged for each roasted coffee. The green pound equivalent price is calculated by converting posted coffee prices to one-pound equivalents and then assuming 15% shrinkage during the roasting process.</span></span></span></p><p class=\"font_9\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: helvetica-w01-roman, helvetica-w02-roman, helvetica-lt-w10-roman, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 63, 63); text-align: justify; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5em; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif; background: transparent;\"><br></span></span></p>',NULL,'2015-08-20 13:18:34',6),(21,' SCAA Report: Blueprint to End Hunger in the Coffee Lands','scaa-report-blueprint-to-end-hunger-in-the-coffee-lands','<br>','<br>',NULL,'2015-08-20 18:16:35',0),(22,' SCAA Report: Blueprint to End Hunger in the Coffee Lands','scaa-report-blueprint-to-end-hunger-in-the-coffee-lands','<p style=\"margin-bottom: 6px; color: rgb(20, 24, 35); font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; line-height: 19.3199996948242px;\"><font size=\"3\">SCAA\'s report entitled “A Blueprint to End Hunger in the Coffee Lands\" highlights an extremely important issue -- farmers inability to earn more than their annual spending needs even with price premiums for fair trade / organic certifications.&nbsp;<span style=\"line-height: 19.3199996948242px;\">The TT Coffee&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 19.3199996948242px;\">Team explores the report and discusses ways in which the industry can move away from the inappropriate use of commodity coffee prices to anchor specialty coffee contracts.</span></font></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 6px; color: rgb(20, 24, 35); font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.3199996948242px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 19.3199996948242px;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 6px; color: rgb(20, 24, 35); font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.3199996948242px;\"><img src=\"http://static.wixstatic.com/media/054a02_6f7146bab1784b31bd45f19fc6dffd06.png_srb_p_302_373_75_22_0.50_1.20_0.00_png_srb\"><br></p>','<font size=\"3\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 63, 63); font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif; line-height: normal;\">This TT Coffee Insight is motivated by a report posted on the SCAA website called&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(68, 63, 63); font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif; line-height: normal; text-decoration: underline; background: transparent;\"><a href=\"http://scaa.org/PDF/SCAA-whitepaper-blueprint-end-hunger-coffeelands.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; cursor: pointer; color: inherit; background: transparent;\">“A Blueprint to End Hunger in the Coffee Lands”</a></span><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 63, 63); font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif; line-height: normal;\">. This report does a good job highlighting an extremely important issue:&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(68, 63, 63); font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif; line-height: normal; font-style: italic; background: transparent;\">“The income that farmers earn from coffee is often less than most farmers’ annual spending needs. Unfortunately, this is true even among farmers who receive a price premium for fair trade or organic certifications (pg. 5).”</span><br></font><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(68, 63, 63); font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif; line-height: normal; font-style: italic; background: transparent;\"><font size=\"3\"><br><img src=\"http://static.wixstatic.com/media/054a02_6f7146bab1784b31bd45f19fc6dffd06.png_srb_p_302_373_75_22_0.50_1.20_0.00_png_srb\" style=\"background-color: transparent;\"><br></font></span></div><div><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(68, 63, 63); font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif; line-height: normal; font-style: italic; background: transparent;\"><font size=\"3\"><br></font></span></div><div><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(68, 63, 63); font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif; line-height: normal; font-style: italic; background: transparent;\"><font size=\"3\"><p class=\"font_8\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">The report also highlights some fine organizations that are working<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;at the edges of specialty coffee markets</span>&nbsp;to provide support for people living in coffee communities. However, its five recommendations [1] do not address the fundamental driver of poverty (and thus hunger) in these communities: the prices that are paid to farmers for their green coffee:&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: italic; background: transparent;\">“In addition to surviving with&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold; background: transparent;\">scarce income</span>, coffee farmers&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold; background: transparent;\">live at the mercy of coffee price fluctuations</span>&nbsp;in the global market, and thus feel an immediate and severe impact on their livelihoods when prices plummet (pg. 5).”</span></p><p class=\"font_8\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">&nbsp;</p><p class=\"font_8\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">Toward the end, the report revisits the issue of green prices paid in specialty coffee markets when it asks protagonists to&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: italic; background: transparent;\">“negotiate contracts with farmers that hedge against extreme price fluctuations (pg. 18).”&nbsp;</span>Here, the obvious reference is to specialty coffee contracts that are set based on prevailing commodity market prices.</p><p class=\"font_8\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">&nbsp;</p><p class=\"font_8\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">Clearly, the month-to-month volatility in commodity coffee prices is a big problem. To see this, consider the following plot of the&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: underline; background: transparent;\"><a href=\"http://www.ico.org/historical/1990%20onwards/PDF/3c-indicator-prices.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; cursor: pointer; color: inherit; background: transparent;\">ICO Composite Price</a></span>&nbsp;over a 25-year period:</p><p class=\"font_8\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><br></p><p class=\"font_8\" style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><img src=\"http://static.wixstatic.com/media/054a02_ce1dca1f39cf425fb5609aaaa90f8eea.jpg_srb_p_527_317_75_22_0.50_1.20_0.00_jpg_srb\"><br></p><p class=\"font_8\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><br></p><p class=\"font_8\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">However, the problems with tying specialty coffee contracts to these commodity prices are actually three-fold: commodity coffee prices are indeed&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold; background: transparent;\">highly volatile</span>, but they are also&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold; background: transparent;\">very low on average</span>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold; background: transparent;\">without a meaningful positive trend</span>. To demonstrate these latter two points, we regress this ICO Composite Price time series against a monthly time trend:<br></p><p class=\"font_8\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><br></p><p class=\"font_8\" style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><img src=\"http://static.wixstatic.com/media/054a02_22a78cba7d274e2994eae061b902ca71.png_srb_p_527_228_75_22_0.50_1.20_0.00_png_srb\"><br></p><p class=\"font_8\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><br></p><p class=\"font_8\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">The intercept in this model suggests that the commodity market settled on a (predicted) price of roughly $0.65 in 1990. The coefficient on the monthly trend variable indicates that since that time, commodity coffee prices increased 0.25 cents per month on average. Thus, by the end of 300 months (from January, 1990 to December, 2014) the predicted price rose to roughly $1.39 per pound.</p><p class=\"font_8\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">&nbsp;</p><p class=\"font_8\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">Of course, these 25 years also experienced price inflation. To account for this, we adjusted the 300 monthly ICO Composite Price observations for changes in the U.S. Consumer Price Index (setting the December, 2014 index to one) and then re-estimate the regression:</p><p class=\"font_8\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><br></p><p class=\"font_8\" style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><img src=\"http://static.wixstatic.com/media/054a02_727fb9653df0480dae24dd2d09de3565.png_srb_p_527_242_75_22_0.50_1.20_0.00_png_srb\"><br></p><p class=\"font_8\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><br></p><p class=\"font_8\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">The intercept in this model suggests that the commodity market settled on a real (predicted) price of $1.27 in 1990. The coefficient on the monthly trend variable tells us that since that time, real coffee prices increased just 0.03 cents per month on average; an amount that is not significantly different from zero. In real terms, predicted commodity coffee prices are just eight cents per pound higher at the end of 2014 than they were at the beginning of 1990. This combination of low and flat prices is evident in the following figure:<br></p><p class=\"font_8\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><br></p><p class=\"font_8\" style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><img src=\"http://static.wixstatic.com/media/054a02_154a9821aa3743809d0a703364080122.jpg_srb_p_527_317_75_22_0.50_1.20_0.00_jpg_srb\"><br></p><p class=\"font_8\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><br></p><p class=\"font_8\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">Returning to the SCAA report, it seems that one of the&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold; background: transparent;\">fundamental</span>&nbsp;causes of sustained poverty and therefore hunger in coffee communities is the (inappropriate) use of commodity coffee prices to anchor specialty coffee contracts. After all, the&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: underline; background: transparent;\"><a href=\"http://www.transparenttradecoffee.org/#!scrpi2/c1fos\" target=\"_self\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; cursor: pointer; color: inherit; background: transparent;\">Specialty Coffee Retail Price Index</a></span>&nbsp;shows that retail prices at the lower end of the specialty coffee market are relatively&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold; background: transparent;\">high and stable</span>, while retail prices at the upper end are&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold; background: transparent;\">high and rising</span>:<br></p><p class=\"font_8\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><br></p><p class=\"font_8\" style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><img src=\"http://static.wixstatic.com/media/054a02_42b446d2baee47829d1785c611cd9814.jpg_srb_p_527_240_75_22_0.50_1.20_0.00_jpg_srb\"><br></p><p class=\"font_8\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><br></p><p class=\"font_8\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">This leads to our preferred&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold; background: transparent;\">Recommendation #1</span>&nbsp;for addressing hunger in coffee communities. If there was a concerted effort to anchor&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold; background: transparent;\">specialty coffee contracts</span>&nbsp;at a&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold; background: transparent;\">minimum&nbsp;</span>of 15 percent of expected retail prices, then green price volatility would virtually disappear. Growers of undifferentiated specialty-grade coffee could expect to receive (at least) $2.06 per pound each and every year.[2] At the same time, growers of higher-quality, differentiated coffees sold at the upper end of the specialty market could expect payments that are tied to end-market valuations, and that average roughly $3.54 per pound. [3]</p><p class=\"font_8\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">&nbsp;</p><p class=\"font_8\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">For affected growers – those growing coffee for the specialty market – this kind of pricing would go a long way toward addressing volatility and mitigating against the thin months mentioned in the SCAA report. And, we believe that this pricing model is consistent with profitable roasting&nbsp;businesses. After all, the eight roasters currently registered on the&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: underline; background: transparent;\"><a href=\"http://www.transparenttradecoffee.org/#!ttcoffees/cjg9\" target=\"_self\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; cursor: pointer; color: inherit; background: transparent;\">TT Coffees page</a></span>report – for a selection of their direct trade coffees – an average effective grower revenue share of more than 20%.</p><p class=\"font_8\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">&nbsp;</p><p class=\"font_8\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">As different readers of the “Blueprint to End Hunger” tackle its various recommendations, it would be extremely beneficial to specialty coffee growers if others began to consider this proposal, and other proposals to anchor green coffee contract negotiations on something other than commodity coffee prices.</p><p class=\"font_8\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">&nbsp;</p><p class=\"font_8\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: italic; background: transparent;\">Notes:</span></span></p><p class=\"font_8\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">&nbsp;</p><p class=\"font_8\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: italic; background: transparent;\">[1] The recommendations include “providing support and technical assistance to maximize food production potential and attain balanced nutrition”, “supporting livelihood diversification so that coffee growers have multiple sources of income and food other than coffee”, “increasing awareness and initiatives to address food insecurity in coffee regions within the coffee Industry”, “developing multi-stakeholder, long-term initiatives”, and “encouraging and supporting research that contributes timely empirical evidence.”</span></span></p><p class=\"font_8\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">&nbsp;</p><p class=\"font_8\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: italic; background: transparent;\">[2] This is 15 percent of the 2015, Q2 SCRPI low-end average price of $16.15 after adjusting for fifteen percent shrinkage during the roasting process.</span></span></p><p class=\"font_8\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">&nbsp;</p><p class=\"font_8\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"font-style: italic; text-align: center; background-color: transparent;\">[3] This is 15 percent of the 2015, Q2 SCRPI high-end average price of $27.73 after adjusting for fifteen percent shrinkage during the roasting process.</span></p></font></span></div>',NULL,'2015-08-20 18:25:06',1);
